348
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:13,250
Send her away

349
00:17:13,250 --> 00:17:14,020
ten seconds before

350
00:17:14,020 --> 00:17:14,720
the time-space overlap ends.

351
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:15,780
She won't find out.

352
00:17:17,849 --> 00:17:19,240
That's a good plan.

353
00:17:19,500 --> 00:17:20,810
I won't help you.

354
00:17:23,180 --> 00:17:23,780
