423
00:20:12,660 --> 00:20:13,380
Because

424
00:20:14,930 --> 00:20:16,330
he has no body and no nose.

425
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:27,090
No.

426
00:20:28,780 --> 00:20:29,540
You're not me.

427
00:20:29,540 --> 00:20:30,660
