428
00:20:31,490 --> 00:20:33,020
What are you good at?

429
00:20:33,430 --> 00:20:34,430
What do you think?

430
00:20:36,380 --> 00:20:37,130
Don't worry.

431
00:20:38,120 --> 00:20:39,320
There's a third move.

