00:20:45,050 --> 00:20:46,970
Open your heart and talk to her.

435
00:20:47,860 --> 00:20:49,430
Tell her

436
00:20:50,110 --> 00:20:50,780
the darkest

437
00:20:51,460 --> 00:20:52,940
