438
00:20:53,420 --> 00:20:54,220
in your heart.

439
00:20:55,060 --> 00:20:57,450
You will get closer

440
00:20:57,490 --> 00:20:59,070
to each other soon.

441
00:21:00,740 --> 00:21:01,540
Let me tell you one more thing.

442
00:21:01,540 --> 00:21:03,000
Something embarrassing.

443
00:21:03,830 --> 00:21:05,110
